tweet: I‚Äôm incredibly optimistic that our big, brawling, risk-taking, dynamic country will continue to lead and succeed ‚Äî but not by protecting powerful incumbents.  Success will come from disruptive ideas that are scary today but expected and even necessary tomorrow.
